platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Merge numbers to create bigger numbers and repeat to avoid gridlock. The formula may be straightforward, but Threes!s simplicity belies an endlessly gratifying and remarkably original game that rewards thoughtful strategy over frenzied swiping. With its lovingly crafted design, whimsical music, and unforgettable gameplay, Threes! is a delightful experience youll return to again and again.
